alluxio.master.keyvalue

Class KeyValueMaster

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.master.AbstractMaster
      • alluxio.master.keyvalue.KeyValueMaster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalCheckpointStreamable, Master

    @ThreadSafe
public final class KeyValueMaster
extends AbstractMaster
    The key-value master stores key-value store information in Alluxio, including the partitions of each key-value store.
